metadata.name: Winter
metadata.description:
Seasonal Flavours embodies a sense of floral femininity and represents the different beauties seen across the seasons - winter, spring, summer and autumn. The calmness of winter, softness of spring, cheerfulness of summer and passion of autumn. Concepts are conveyed through the distinct colours that represent each season. Each woman has her own colour and aura, and no flower resembles the other. 

Winter Season
Digital Painting | 2020
Part of Seasonal Flavours
4000 x 4000
1 of 1 edition
